  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your primal savagery grants you the following benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Savage Physical Defense:</strong> You gain access to the following&nbsp;<strong>PD </strong>formula while not wearing Armor:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>8 + Combat Mastery + Agility + Prime.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Fast Movement:</strong> You gain +1 Speed while not wearing Armor.</p>\n<p><strong>Mighty Leap: </strong>You can use your Might instead of Agility to determine your Jump Distance and the damage you take&nbsp;from Falling.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip:&nbsp;</strong>You can select \"Savage Defence\" on Physical Defence Configuration on your Character sheet. You can select \"Might\" as a Jump Attribute on Jump Configuration on your Character sheet.</em></p>",
